platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: We're in it for the music

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love a good Mountain Dew–fueled debate over the best way to use Magic Missile, and if you’re right there with us, you won’t be able to resist this card-based adventure either. The dialogue targets RPG clichés (“Rats? How original!”) with hilarious sarcasm, but the gameplay is what really grabbed us. Instead of controlling adventurers, you snap cards onto graph paper, building out dungeons that they automatically explore, loot, and die in. (Oops.) We were torn between rooting for them and mischievously seeing how much trouble we could cause…
